{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/national-minimum-wage-rates.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/national-minimum-wage-rates","title":"National Minimum Wage rates","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"1859","business_proposition":false,"description":"The National Minimum Wage rates valid from 1 October 2012 - NMW, age, apprentices ","alternative_title":"","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>The National Minimum Wage rate per hour depends on your age and whether you’re an apprentice - it’s valid from 1 October each year.</p>\n</div>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Year</th>\n      <th>21 and over</th>\n      <th>18 to 20</th>\n      <th>Under 18</th>\n      <th>Apprentice</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><strong>2012 (current rate)</strong></td>\n      <td><strong>£6.19</strong></td>\n      <td><strong>£4.98</strong></td>\n      <td><strong>£3.68</strong></td>\n      <td><strong>£2.65</strong></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>2011</td>\n      <td>£6.08</td>\n      <td>£4.98</td>\n      <td>£3.68</td>\n      <td>£2.60</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>2010</td>\n      <td>£5.93</td>\n      <td>£4.92</td>\n      <td>£3.64</td>\n      <td>£2.50</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>The age groups were different before 2010. There were no National Minimum Wage rates for apprentices.</p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Year</th>\n      <th>22 and over</th>\n      <th>18 to 21</th>\n      <th>Under 18</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>2009</td>\n      <td>£5.80</td>\n      <td>£4.83</td>\n      <td>£3.57</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>2008</td>\n      <td>£5.73</td>\n      <td>£4.77</td>\n      <td>£3.53</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>2007</td>\n      <td>£5.52</td>\n      <td>£4.60</td>\n      <td>£3.40</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>2006</td>\n      <td>£5.35</td>\n      <td>£4.45</td>\n      <td>£3.30</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n   